{
  "stem": "25773.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was almost the end of '42, because the selections were taking place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know anything which was happening in the big ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there-- our small ghetto was-- the selections were all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But when you went outside, it was a grim view.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PHONE RINGS] Don't take any notice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they said always-- [PHONE RINGS] Say I'm not at home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was all the time were big placards for-- unless it's my daughter, if it's my daughter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was written, verboten, verboten, verboten.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Forbidden, forbidden.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Big, big, big placards and saying-- this is verboten, verboten, always.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And gray and poor-looking, and sort of, you know, the trams.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were struck by extreme poverty and foreboding feeling of-- all unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I made my way-- I think it was early, very early-- and I made to my way to this street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It, I think-- there was [NON-ENGLISH] Street-- it was called Golden Street-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was given by my friend [NON-ENGLISH] you know, to keep with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Money.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I could go to a little shop and buy myself a bun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for fear of being recognized or something like that, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, eventually, like midday, slowly, slowly-- I couldn't recognize-- because it was-- the walls were the whole-- my own orientation, I couldn't orientate myself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was disorientated, which way to go, how to find the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was afraid to approach anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where is the place?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually I found it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I asked somebody who was on the street, looked, looked a poor man or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was not afraid of him, and he directed me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I went into this building-- it was on the second floor or something-- I rang the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
